          <h3>Day 1: Quick Overnight Oats</h3>
          <table class="responsive-table">
            <tr><th>Ingredients</th><th>Instructions</th></tr>
            <tr>
              <td>
                <ul>
                  <li>1/2 cup rolled oats</li>
                  <li>1/2 cup unsweetened almond milk</li>
                  <li>1/2 banana, sliced</li>
                  <li>1 tablespoon honey</li>
                  <li>Pinch of salt</li>
                  <li>Top with nuts or seeds (optional)</li>
                </ul>
              </td>
              <td>Combine all ingredients in a jar or container. Refrigerate overnight and enjoy in the morning.</td>
            </tr>
          </table>
